  "texts": [
    "The \"Communication Framework\" was represented by each student's inner meta-reflection, which occurred during the various co-creation sessions with the Gen AI tools, to ensure the results were consistent with the project and after the European Journal of Cultural Management and Policy",
    "The interpretation of the Artificial A(i)rchive results through the application of the two matrices allowed us to identify the cocreation dynamics common to the groups participating in the laboratory.",
    "Mapping the integration of Gen AI tools in the fashion design process also led to a preliminary reflection on the alignment between the capabilities of the tested instruments and the application domain requirements.",
    "This consistency was analysed through the levels of \"Artefact Knowledge,\" \"Design Intuition\" and \"Design Language,\" which delineate how knowledge in design is structured, acquired and transferred (Thoring et al., 2023).",
    "The resulting discussion can contribute to the debate around human-AI co-creation and the intersection of natural and artificial creativity, specifically in fashion design."
